{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"clay-spray-signal","description":"## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Reconcile infra/terraform-github with the live gerrit-mirror-lock-main ruleset (id 18402431) so terraform plan shows no changes (or import it).\n- [ ] Replace the check deploy_key_present block (only WARNs) with a lifecycle precondition that aborts apply if the replication deploy key is absent (WS7 plan-review adv 7).\n- [ ] Add a scheduled drift check that the ruleset stays active + deploy-key-only.\n\n## Context\nWS7 applied the lock via gh-api, not terraform. The ssm snapshot id (18048287) differs from the deleted legacy (18306946) and the new ruleset (18402431); reconcile runbook + terraform to reality.","id":"8ccf-f4e4-ad2d-480d","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Terraform-github state reconcile + drift detection for the mirror-lock ruleset"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782943638620411001,"uuid":"1bff3f1d-40f8-4ebe-8205-4da7443dd747"}